4Geeks Academy offers a Cybersecurity Bootcamp designed for individuals with no prior knowledge, aiming to become cybersecurity specialists. Over 16 weeks, students will engage in three live online classes per week, with class sizes limited to 16 participants. The program covers key areas such as Windows and Linux administration, cloud security, penetration testing, and risk management, while also ensuring compliance with international standards like ISO 27001 and NIST. Upon completion, students earn a recognized 4Geeks Completion Certificate. The curriculum is available in both English and Spanish. For more information, visit [4Geeks Academy](https://4geeksacademy.com/us/coding-bootcamps/cybersecurity). stop